1.0.name: wordpress/woocommerce-paysius
1.0.description:
Add Paysius gateway to WooCommerce

WooCommerce Paysius is a Bitcoin payment gateway for WooCommerce.

Please notice that WooCommerce must be installed and actived.

The WooCommerce Paysius plugin was developed without any incentive from Paysius. None of the plugin developer has ties to this company.
